               <p>WILLIAM SHEARMAN. On the 23d of March, in the evening, I left a coat at the bar of the <placeName id="t18280410-239-crimeloc1278">Nelson's Head public-house, Hackney-road</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18280410-239-crimeloc1278" type="placeName" value="Nelson's Head public-house, Hackney-road"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18280410-239-crimeloc1278" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-239-off1276 t18280410-239-crimeloc1278"></join>, while I took a pint of beer; I did not see it taken.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280410-239-person1333">
                  JOSEPH 
                  THIMBLEBY
               <interp inst="t18280410-239-person1333" type="surname" value="THIMBLEBY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280410-239-person1333" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280410-239-person1333" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker. This coat was pawned with me on the 24th of March, by the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280410-239-person1334">
                  ELIZABETH 
                  HANNAH WRIGHT
               <interp inst="t18280410-239-person1334" type="surname" value="HANNAH WRIGHT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280410-239-person1334" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280410-239-person1334" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live at the Nelson's Head. On the 23d of March, about half-past ten o'clock at night, I was in the parlour, and saw the prisoner coming out of the bar - he turned by the counter; I went and looked at the till - that was all right; I did not think of the coat till the prosecutor applied for it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280410-239-person1335">
                  GEORGE 
                  SMITH
               <interp inst="t18280410-239-person1335" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
